text.text: I am having trouble with my health assessment

differences.description:
Page mismatch:
Expected: 
Actual:   Start Page

differences.actualValue: Thank you for reaching out to us. I apologize for the issues you are experiencing with the program. It is recommended you use the Google Chrome web browser. Please clear the cache and cookies, by clicking the three dots in the upper right corner of the browser. Then click Settings; under Privacy and Security, click Delete Browsing Data. Make sure All Time is selected in the Time Range box; only check the Browsing History, Cookies and Other Site Data, and Cached Images and Files boxes. Once the browsing data has cleared, please close and re-open your browser and try again to complete the Health Assessment. If this does not solve the problem, you may also complete the Health Assessment using the AlwaysOn app. Tap the clipboard icon to access the Health Assessment on the app. Please let me know if you are unsuccessful so that we can further troubleshoot.
